title: Caboose Cafe and Bakery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Italian, Beer/Wine, Bakery, Ethiopian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Although the menu is mostly meat & dairy American and Italian entrees, it also features several vegan Ethiopian dishes a la carte or as a vegan sampler for one or two diners with miser watt, kik alitcha, gomen, cabbage, and Ethiopian fosolakia served with injera bread. Free Wi-Fi.
